stake(nft_id: int, amount: int, is_estimate: bool = False, gas: int = 0, gas_price: int = 0, nonce: int = 0) → TransactionReceipt | int[source]

Stakes an amount for a given NFT ID in the stake pool.

Parameters:

  • nft_id – The NFT ID to stake for

  • amount – The amount to stake

  • is_estimate – If True, returns the estimated gas for the transaction

  • gas – The gas limit for the transaction

  • gas_price – The gas price for the transaction

  • nonce – The nonce for the transaction

Returns:

The transaction receipt if not estimating gas, otherwise the estimated gas

Unstakes an amount for a given NFT ID from the stake pool.

Parameters:

  • nft_id – The NFT ID to unstake from

  • amount – The amount to unstake

  • is_estimate – If True, returns the estimated gas for the transaction

  • gas – The gas limit for the transaction

  • gas_price – The gas price for the transaction

  • nonce – The nonce for the transaction

Returns:

The transaction receipt if not estimating gas, otherwise the estimated gas
